ORIGINAL WORK NOTICE:
This project introduces the concept of Universal Code Mode - a novel approach
to reducing LLM token usage when working with multiple API types (MCP, REST,
GraphQL, databases) by generating optimized TypeScript wrappers.

First public release: November 2025
Original implementation date: November 2025

The universal adapter pattern, .agent-ready.json discovery mechanism, and
multi-source code generation approach are original contributions of this project.

